rationale: This trade is a classic win-win, addressing core needs for both teams. You receive a massive upgrade at your TE position with the elite Trey McBride and add a strong RB2 in D'Andre Swift. In return, I get a true RB1 in Alvin Kamara and a top-tier WR in Tee Higgins, significantly improving my starting lineup. Both our teams become stronger contenders.
